@page "/about"

<PageTitle>HellBlaze | About</PageTitle>


<div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-header">
        <h1>HellBlaze</h1>
        <p class="tagline">A comprehensive loadout randomiser tool for Helldivers 2</p>
    </div>

    <section class="about-section">
        <h2>About This Tool</h2>
        <p>
            HellBlaze is a fan-made web application designed to help Helldivers inject some more fun back into their
            games.
            No more taking your favourites. No more only playing optimally! Try out some randomised loadouts that you'd
            never
            think of before.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
        <h2>How to Use</h2>
        <div class="usage-steps">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h3>Choose your style of randomisation</h3>
                    <p>Increasing multiplier sliders will increase the chance of seeing that style of
                        weapon/stratagem.</p>
                    <p>Increase the base (or reduce your multipliers) to get a wider selection of items</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h3>Create Your Squad</h3>
                    <p>Add up to four divers to your squad and customize their owned warbonds. You can click their names
                        to edit them, too.</p>
                    <p>You can apply a filter so that no diver gets the same stratagem (or it is limited to
                        1,2,3...)</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h3>Optimize Loadouts</h3>
                    <p>Filter items by warbond and hit randomise. Lock your loadout by hitting ready. (Useful if someone
                        owns less content)</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">4</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h3>Take on the Daily Challenge</h3>
                    <p>The daily challenge is seeded and resets each UTC day. It'd a bit fiddly if you start changing
                        available warbonds, though</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Latest Updates</h2>
        <div class="updates-container">
            <div class="update-entry">
                <div class="update-version">v1.0.0</div>
                <div class="update-date">8 May 2025</div>
                <div class="update-details">
                    <h4>Initial Commit</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Randomiser initial release</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section github-section">
        <h2>Contribute & Follow</h2>
        <p>
            HellBlaze is an open-source project. You can contribute, report issues, or request features on GitHub.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/janLalawa/Hellblaze/" target="_blank" class="github-button">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                 stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                 class="feather feather-github">
                <path
                    d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>View on GitHub</span>
        </a>
    </section>

    <footer class="about-footer">
        <p>
            HellBlaze is a fan-made tool and is not affiliated with Arrowhead Game Studios or PlayStation Studios.
            Helldivers 2 and all related properties are trademarks of their respective owners.
        </p>
        <p>
            &copy; @DateTime.Now.Year - HellBlaze
        </p>
    </footer>
</div>

